1,532 2. Notre Dame (12) 11-1-0 1,478 3. Nebraska 11-1-0 1,418 4. Auburn (4) 
11-0-0 1,375 5. Florida 11-2-0 1,307 6. Wisconsin 10-1-1 1,228 7. West Virginia 
11-1-0 1,090 8. Penn St. 10-2-0 1,074 9. Texas A&M 10-2-0 1,043 10. Arizona 
10-2-0 992  
</P>
